      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Product / Project Library\n\nThis package captures product semantics that sit adjacent to planning without duplicating it.\n\nV1 product-specific classes:\n- `problem`\n- `user-need`\n- `initiative`\n- `feature`\n- `metric`\n\nPlanning continues to supply shared classes like `decision`, `constraint`, `risk`, and `open-question`.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
