      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 220,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Integration Note\n\nThis nodeset is meant to compose with planning, not replace it.\n\nTypical relationships:\n- `feature` solves `problem`\n- `feature` serves `user-need`\n- `initiative` groups `feature`\n- `metric` measures `feature` or `initiative`",
        "_classBinding": {
